{
  "id": null,
  "uid": "valkey-cache",
  "title": "Valkey Cache",
  "description": "Cache health, hit rate, memory, evictions, replication — sourced from redis-exporter via Prometheus. ProxySQL query cache stats: see text panel below.",
  "tags": ["valkey", "cache", "dbre", "lab"],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": {"from": "now-1h", "to": "now"},
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "panels": [

    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Valkey Up",
      "description": "1 = up, 0 = down",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 4, "h": 4},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr": "redis_up", "legendFormat": "valkey", "refId": "A"}],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [{"type": "value", "options": {
            "0": {"text": "DOWN", "color": "red", "index": 0},
            "1": {"text": "UP",   "color": "green", "index": 1}
          }}],
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"color": "red", "value": null},
            {"color": "green", "value": 1}
          ]},
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}
        }
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "gauge",
      "title": "Cache Hit Rate",
      "description": "hits / (hits + misses) over last 2 min. <80% = investigate, <50% = cache not effective",
      "gridPos": {"x": 4, "y": 0, "w": 5, "h": 4},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "100 * rate(redis_keyspace_hits_total[2m]) / (rate(redis_keyspace_hits_total[2m]) + rate(redis_keyspace_misses_total[2m]) + 0.001)",
        "legendFormat": "hit rate %",
        "refId": "A"
      }],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"color": "red",    "value": null},
            {"color": "orange", "value": 50},
            {"color": "yellow", "value": 80},
            {"color": "green",  "value": 95}
          ]},
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}
        }
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Memory Used",
      "description": "Current RSS memory. Cap = 256 MB (allkeys-lru eviction kicks in at limit)",
      "gridPos": {"x": 9, "y": 0, "w": 5, "h": 4},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr": "redis_memory_used_bytes", "legendFormat": "used", "refId": "A"}],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "orientation": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "bytes",
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"color": "green",  "value": null},
            {"color": "yellow", "value": 209715200},
            {"color": "red",    "value": 251658240}
          ]},
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}
        }
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Total Keys",
      "description": "Keys currently in all databases",
      "gridPos": {"x": 14, "y": 0, "w": 4, "h": 4},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr": "sum(redis_db_keys)", "legendFormat": "keys", "refId": "A"}],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "orientation": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "blue", "value": null}]},
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}
        }
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Evictions / s",
      "description": "Rate of key evictions due to maxmemory policy. Sustained evictions = memory pressure — consider increasing limit or reducing TTLs",
      "gridPos": {"x": 18, "y": 0, "w": 6, "h": 4},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr": "rate(redis_evicted_keys_total[2m])", "legendFormat": "evictions/s", "refId": "A"}],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "orientation": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"color": "green",  "value": null},
            {"color": "yellow", "value": 1},
            {"color": "red",    "value": 100}
          ]},
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}
        }
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Cache Hits vs Misses (rate/s)",
      "description": "Hits = served from cache (no DB). Misses = forwarded to database. Healthy ratio: hits >> misses after warm-up.",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 4, "w": 12, "h": 8},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(redis_keyspace_hits_total[1m])",
          "legendFormat": "hits/s",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "rate(redis_keyspace_misses_total[1m])",
          "legendFormat": "misses/s",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "options": {"tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"unit": "ops"},
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "hits/s"},
            "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"fixedColor": "green", "mode": "fixed"}}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "misses/s"},
            "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"fixedColor": "orange", "mode": "fixed"}}]
          }
        ]
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Commands Processed / s",
      "description": "Total Valkey operations per second — GET, SET, HGET, EXPIRE, etc.",
      "gridPos": {"x": 12, "y": 4, "w": 12, "h": 8},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "rate(redis_commands_processed_total[1m])",
        "legendFormat": "ops/s",
        "refId": "A"
      }],
      "options": {"tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "ops"}}
    },

    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hit Rate % over time",
      "description": "Rolling 2-min hit rate. Dip = new query patterns or cold start after restart.",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 12, "w": 12, "h": 8},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "100 * rate(redis_keyspace_hits_total[2m]) / (rate(redis_keyspace_hits_total[2m]) + rate(redis_keyspace_misses_total[2m]) + 0.001)",
        "legendFormat": "hit rate %",
        "refId": "A"
      }],
      "options": {"tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"color": "red",    "value": null},
            {"color": "orange", "value": 50},
            {"color": "yellow", "value": 80},
            {"color": "green",  "value": 95}
          ]},
          "custom": {
            "thresholdsStyle": {"mode": "area"}
          }
        }
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Memory Usage over time",
      "description": "Used memory vs 256 MB cap. When used approaches cap, allkeys-lru starts evicting.",
      "gridPos": {"x": 12, "y": 12, "w": 12, "h": 8},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "redis_memory_used_bytes",
          "legendFormat": "used",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "redis_maxmemory_bytes",
          "legendFormat": "cap (256MB)",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "options": {"tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"unit": "bytes"},
        "overrides": [{
          "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "cap (256MB)"},
          "properties": [
            {"id": "color", "value": {"fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed"}},
            {"id": "custom.lineStyle", "value": {"dash": [10, 10], "fill": "dash"}},
            {"id": "custom.lineWidth", "value": 1}
          ]
        }]
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Keys with TTL",
      "description": "Expiring keys — these will auto-evict on TTL expiry (keyspace notification event)",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 20, "w": 5, "h": 4},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr": "sum(redis_db_keys_expiring)", "legendFormat": "expiring", "refId": "A"}],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "orientation": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "blue", "value": null}]},
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}
        }
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Connected Clients",
      "description": "Active Valkey client connections. Spike = connection leak or traffic burst.",
      "gridPos": {"x": 5, "y": 20, "w": 5, "h": 4},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr": "redis_connected_clients", "legendFormat": "clients", "refId": "A"}],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "orientation": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"color": "green",  "value": null},
            {"color": "yellow", "value": 50},
            {"color": "red",    "value": 100}
          ]},
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}
        }
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Connected Replicas",
      "description": "Number of replicas currently connected and replicating",
      "gridPos": {"x": 10, "y": 20, "w": 5, "h": 4},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr": "redis_replication_connected_slaves", "legendFormat": "replicas", "refId": "A"}],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "orientation": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [{"type": "value", "options": {
            "0": {"text": "0 — no replica", "color": "orange", "index": 0},
            "1": {"text": "1 replica OK",   "color": "green",  "index": 1}
          }}],
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"color": "orange", "value": null},
            {"color": "green",  "value": 1}
          ]},
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}
        }
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Evictions over time",
      "description": "Keys evicted per second by LRU policy. Sustained pressure = tune maxmemory or TTLs.",
      "gridPos": {"x": 15, "y": 20, "w": 9, "h": 4},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr": "rate(redis_evicted_keys_total[1m])", "legendFormat": "evictions/s", "refId": "A"}],
      "options": {"tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "custom": {"fillOpacity": 20},
          "color": {"fixedColor": "orange", "mode": "fixed"}
        }
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 14,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "ProxySQL Query Cache — how to check",
      "description": "ProxySQL does not expose Prometheus metrics; query the admin interface directly",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 24, "w": 24, "h": 6},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## ProxySQL built-in query cache\n\nProxySQL caches `SELECT … FROM products` (30 s TTL) and `SELECT COUNT(…)` (5 s TTL) transparently — the app sends normal SQL, ProxySQL serves from memory without touching MySQL.\n\nCheck via the ProxySQL admin port (6032):\n\n```sql\n-- Connect: mysql -u admin -padminpass -h 127.0.0.1 -P 6032\n\n-- Cache counters\nSELECT Variable_Name, Variable_Value\nFROM stats_mysql_global\nWHERE Variable_Name LIKE 'Query_Cache%';\n-- Query_Cache_count_GET     total lookups\n-- Query_Cache_count_GET_OK  hits   →  hit rate = GET_OK / GET\n-- Query_Cache_count_SET     misses (result stored)\n-- Query_Cache_Entries       current cached entries\n-- Query_Cache_Memory_bytes  memory used by cache\n\n-- Per-query breakdown (cache_entries > 0 = cached)\nSELECT hostgroup, digest_text, count_star, cache_entries, sum_time\nFROM stats_mysql_query_digest\nWHERE digest_text LIKE '%products%' OR digest_text LIKE '%COUNT%'\nORDER BY count_star DESC LIMIT 10;\n\n-- Flush cache without restart\nPROXYSQL FLUSH QUERY CACHE;\n```\n\nOr from the terminal: `docker exec proxysql mysql -u admin -padminpass -h 127.0.0.1 -P 6032 -e \"SELECT * FROM stats_mysql_global WHERE Variable_Name LIKE 'Query_Cache%';\"`"
      }
    }

  ],

  "templating": {"list": []},
  "annotations": {"list": []},
  "links": [
    {"title": "MySQL Overview",    "url": "/d/mysql-overview",    "type": "link", "targetBlank": false},
    {"title": "MySQL Processlist", "url": "/d/mysql-processlist", "type": "link", "targetBlank": false}
  ]
}
